{
  "id": "69f58b700a67f8ccebdd2bb3",
  "title": "普通に自分が嫌だと思うことはやらないほうが良い",
  "created": 1777699697,
  "updated": 1777700112,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f58b700a67f8ccebdd2bb3",
      "text": "普通に自分が嫌だと思うことはやらないほうが良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec3f9",
      "text": "from [2026/04/29]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec3fa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777700112
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec3fb",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec3fc",
      "text": " やっぱり同じようなページが200並ぶのはやり過ぎでした。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec3fd",
      "text": "\t普通に自分が嫌だと思うことはやらないほうが良い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec3fe",
      "text": "\t\t自分で「うへぇ」と思いながらやるのって、結局アカンし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec3ff",
      "text": "\t\t損得で言えば損",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec400",
      "text": "\t\t道理的には謎",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec401",
      "text": "\t\t\t誰がそんなこと望んでいるんだと思いながらやるのは筋違い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec402",
      "text": "\t\t\t自分の中では説明できても普通に人から見たら奇行",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec403",
      "text": "\t\tアレだ。[狂人の真似とて大路を走らば、即ち狂人なり]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    },
    {
      "id": "69f58b700000000000aec404",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777699697,
      "updated": 1777699697
    }
  ]
}